      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/17863957.Ibn_Khaldun">About Ibn Khaldun</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/17863957.Ibn_Khaldun"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1535380310p3/17863957.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/17863957.Ibn_Khaldun">Ibn Khaldun
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
1,281
followers
</div>

